{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"df5720ae11","title":"第十三章 上海“文革”时期的水产品生产和供应","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"c27fd5aa57","index":0,"year":2011,"month":4,"day":null,"articleId":"df5720ae11"}],"tags":[{"id":"44f81d89d9","name":"上海辞书出版社","type":"出版方/发行方"},{"id":"56a499f88d","name":"上海文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"994fc035d4","name":"工业战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","name":"非常与正常——上海“文革”时期的社会生活（下）（上海辞书出版社2011年）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"金大陆著，上海辞书出版社2011年","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"fcdfaa8639","name":"金大陆"}]},"publication_details":{"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7974f3e7cc","type":"paragraph","text":"第十三章上海“文革”时期的水产品生产和供应","index":0,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"ea6e6ab3f4","type":"paragraph","text":"一、资源与资源链的断裂","index":1,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"f555a93518","type":"paragraph","text":"上海称“沪”（），“”即为一种捕鱼工具，可见上海地区的渔业历史悠久，渔业资源丰富，其主要构成为海洋渔业资源、长江渔业资源和内河渔业资源。","index":2,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"e8a71573f5","type":"paragraph","text":"海洋渔业资源：上海浙临东海，一年四季鱼汛不断，“春有黄鱼，夏有乌贼，秋有海，冬有带鱼”。60年代后期，上海大黄鱼年产量在2000吨至3000吨左右，70年代前期，年产量直线上升到4000吨至8000吨左右，1975年甚至突破1万吨（然而，这怡恰是“突变前的聚力收缩”）。1976年后大黄鱼产量急剧下降，下降到年均产量1000吨至2000吨的水平。80年代年产只有几百吨，1990年仅为50吨。1]60年代前期，上海小黄鱼年产量保持在2.2万吨～2.5万吨。60年代后期年产量下降，如1969年为2000吨。此后有所回升，如1974年为1.5万吨（然而，这恰怡又是“突变前的聚力收缩”），197","index":3,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"2d3f60d562","type":"paragraph","text":"PDG年后上海小黄鱼便不成渔汛。2]乌贼在5-7月的长江口近海成汛1964年至1973年产量为1000吨至4000吨，此后产量下滑，1974年至1977年，年产量已不足1000吨。3]冬季带鱼在长江口海区南侧形成渔场，是上海最主要的食用海水鱼。60年代年产量为2.5万至6.4万吨；70年代上升到4.5万至8.5万吨（此为1973年数据。然而，这恰恰又是“突变前的聚力收缩”的实证）。因自1973年以后，“大条带鱼数量少，带丝相对增加”。4]至80年代后，上海带鱼产量呈下降超势，且鱼体小型化显著，1龄鱼占90%以上，带鱼资源衰退。","index":4,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"d478cf8a58","type":"paragraph","text":"中年以上的上海居民应该记忆犹新，70年代初，上海的菜场里冒出了两种水产新品，那就是1971年与1973年初，上海海洋渔业公司的渔轮分别在石东和鱼外渔场，捕获到高网产的青条鱼（网产2吨～8吨）和绿马面鱼（网产12吨），并迅速组织投产。据统计，1971年捕获青条鱼4100吨，占年总产量的4.1%；1972年为4万吨，占年总产量的32.98%；1974年年产绿鳍马面鱼1.5万吨，占年总产量的14%，此后产量逐年上升，1978年高达6万吨，占年总产量的38.3%。5]应该承认，青条鱼、绿马面鱼并不适宜上海人精细的口味，市场还采取了种种优惠的推销措施（同时，大量开发油炸马面鱼瓶装罐头，1972年达到911.74吨；1974年达到1021.40吨）。就此，上海“文革”期间的海洋水产呈现出传统资源衰退、新兴品种突起的情状。","index":5,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"3328a51c23","type":"paragraph","text":"2","index":6,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"c0a3d1699b","type":"paragraph","text":"PDG青条鱼","index":7,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"fbea103654","type":"paragraph","text":"绿马面鱼","index":8,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"9e1d7ead9a","type":"paragraph","text":"长江渔业资源：长江口是著名的河口渔业区，主要水产品有刀解、风解（俗称“烤子鱼”）、银鱼（俗称“米丈鱼”）和中华绒蟹（俗称“崇明蟹”）。每年3-4月万在长江口形成渔汛。据统计，1973年和1974年时，产量分别高达391吨和334吨。1975年时，产量健降至164吨，此后便逐年下降。接着，每年4月至6月为风盛渔期。“文革”期间平均年产量为1125吨，如1970年为1266吨，1975年为1017吨，产量虽有起伏，但资源比较稳定。60年代银鱼产量较高，至1971年前基本保持年产200吨至300吨左右，如1965年产251吨1970年为274吨。1972年起银鱼产量明显下降，多数年份不到100吨，如1975年时只有65吨。70年代以来，由于水质污染严重，捕捞产量逐年减少。6]","index":9,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"e757f0ab53","type":"paragraph","text":"长江口成蟹捕捞集中在每年秋冬李。50年代至60年代上半期年产量在100吨左右波动。1967年起急剧下降，至1969年时年产仅1~2吨。此后，市水产局试验人员研究了壁回游、繁殖、发育、生长等规律，从崇明捕捞苗流放内河天然水域成功，使上海的河壁产量直线上升。171971年时，年产量回升至19吨，1975年为45吨，1976年甚至达到114吨。[8]","index":10,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"fbcb413650","type":"paragraph","text":"内河渔业资源：上海地区水系交错，野生淡水鱼类资源丰富，计有85种。上海内河捕捞主要集中在黄浦江沿岸的松江、奉贤、金山、上海、宝山、川沙等县和青浦西部地区。50年代初，黄浦江水质尚好，年产量为30吨～50吨。至1966年前年产量仍在1万吨左右70年代开始，黄浦江自龙华以下水质恶化，鱼、虾基本绝迹，“1976年后基本停止黄浦江捕鱼生产”。9]苏州河、蕴藻浜的命运亦然。如50年代时，上海黄渡渔民在苏州河上游捕捞鱼虾贝类，仅贝类产量就可","index":11,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"587e222bc6","type":"paragraph","text":"PDG达300多吨。蕴藻滨水质丰沛，常年有渔民以捕捞为生。60年代后，皆因鱼虾资源衰竭而停息。上海青浦地区的野生鱼捕捞，也从1965年的763.2吨下降到1975年的284.4吨。10]1973年农林部召开全国会议，提出“发展城郊养鱼”的要求。上海便着手制定建设精养鱼塘商品基地规划，至1975年春上海已建成精养鱼塘333公项（合5千亩）。11就此，上海内河渔业完成了从野生捕捞到淡水养殖的格局转化。12]","index":12,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"56e8f8656b","type":"paragraph","text":"吴淞江上的内河捕捞","index":13,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"c0e4c73fe6","type":"paragraph","text":"心","index":14,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"2bb51427b7","type":"paragraph","text":"②","index":15,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"cc88862f97","type":"paragraph","text":"精养鱼塘综上所述，就上海地区渔业资源和生产情况而言，可引出一个令","index":16,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"c0ba46c8f4","type":"paragraph","text":"PDG人惊弦的结论—一正是在整个“文革”时期（集中发生在70年代），除了极少数鱼品如凤解等资源相对稳定外，绝大多数的鱼类资源衰退了，甚至枯委了，且全面发生在海洋、长江和内河等三大水域。那么，这究竞是天灾还是人褐？具体指认是物种资源的退化，还是生存环境的恶化，抑或与“文革”运动有什么关联？现以海洋渔业为主说明，看表一：","index":17,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"afba55a670","type":"paragraph","text":"表一上海“文革”时期海洋渔业公司船只、产量情况表","index":18,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"295bf78355","type":"paragraph","text":"单位：、吨年份1966","index":19,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"ca2a8da847","type":"paragraph","text":"1967196819691970197119721973197419751976205","index":20,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"636ffddf28","type":"paragraph","text":"198","index":21,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"5838bf04c7","type":"paragraph","text":"187","index":22,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"2b10d7311f","type":"paragraph","text":"200船只211","index":23,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"84e866fc3c","type":"paragraph","text":"228","index":24,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"4c68e992d5","type":"paragraph","text":"263","index":25,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"1ee1978a0d","type":"paragraph","text":"265","index":26,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"d51b71a22b","type":"paragraph","text":"266255","index":27,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"494e04040e","type":"paragraph","text":"255产量73042528445449272803","index":28,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"57caf3fcf4","type":"paragraph","text":"87543100082 120307 127039 112285 10869191698资料来源：顾惠庭：《上海渔业志》，第319页。","index":29,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"9d726a5419","type":"paragraph","text":"由表一可知：上海“文革”时期海洋渔业的船只数与产量大致呈现正相关的联系。其实，“文革”初期上海海洋渔业公司曾一度“停船闹革命”，直接导致海洋水产品由1966年的7万多吨下降至1967年、1968年的5万多吨。1970年至1972年，上海投资6000多万元新建渔轮84艘，不仅使所属渔轮总吨位达37275吨，更因新建渔轮设备齐全，性能先进，全面提高了作业能力。与此同时，上海郊县各渔业公社在国家无息贷款的扶持下，完成了渔船机动化的改造，使海洋机帆渔船数达历史最高的444。13]同期，上海郊县的长江、内河木质渔船开始装备动力机械，数量从1970年的40渔船，快速增至1976年的638艘。14]就此，上海海洋渔业生产拐进了一个“增产与危机”并存的轨道，无其表现在1970年至1973年间，年产量由8万多吨增至12万多吨。下面请看上海报纸ppG的同期报道渔船","index":30,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"eba5b25989","type":"paragraph","text":"表二","index":31,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"ca49dc0426","type":"paragraph","text":"1970年至1973年上海报纸关于渔业生产的报道日期","index":32,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"6b4e6c0107","type":"paragraph","text":"报纸","index":33,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"c32ba051ba","type":"paragraph","text":"标题","index":34,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"e81eeb2df8","type":"paragraph","text":"内","index":35,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"61ebd1a218","type":"paragraph","text":"容“4月上半月海上捕鱼生产比去年4月","index":36,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"04f2e4fe1b","type":"paragraph","text":"全月的总产量增加21%”，“一对渔轮","index":37,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"0bf2c893df","type":"paragraph","text":"《上半月海上捕鱼一网就捕到十多万厅大黄鱼”，“有一1970.4.19《解放日报》","index":38,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"459baff9b9","type":"paragraph","text":"生产获得大丰收》","index":39,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"93e761340f","type":"paragraph","text":"网捕到近二十万斤鱼，调运兄弟渔轮奋战21个小时，将这一网鱼全部装","index":40,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"fa92c68f0c","type":"paragraph","text":"上船”。","index":41,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"12214585c0","type":"paragraph","text":"《本市渔业工人夺1970年8月份“月产量比去年同期增1970.9.30《文汇报》","index":42,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"2a3fd20b06","type":"paragraph","text":"高产迎接国庆》","index":43,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"bdb0743995","type":"paragraph","text":"加了50%”。旺季时“放网快，起网快，处理鱼类快，","index":44,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"58d95114f2","type":"paragraph","text":"减少停港时间”：淡季时，延长航次，增","index":45,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"9eba6fbec7","type":"paragraph","text":"《本市渔业生产取加网次，做到“淡季不淡，旺季更旺”1972.2.20《解放日报》","index":46,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"8483ee6fec","type":"paragraph","text":"“遵照毛主席“大风大浪也不可怕的得很大成绩》","index":47,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"1862d08d99","type":"paragraph","text":"教导，采取“抢风前，追风尾的办法，夺得了高产”。","index":48,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"048edeeadb","type":"paragraph","text":"因渔网被推进器缠住，船长带头跳进","index":49,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"4deb291db5","type":"paragraph","text":"《渔业工人破浪前1972.10.15《文汇报》","index":50,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"85ad9c9de0","type":"paragraph","text":"大海，在大海中奋战9小时，夺回了五详》","index":51,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"35243fe531","type":"paragraph","text":"千多斤大黄鱼。","index":52,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"5727e9adde","type":"paragraph","text":"（续表）","index":53,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"afe3bd2a78","type":"paragraph","text":"内容报纸","index":54,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"455c84ae0c","type":"paragraph","text":"标题日期","index":55,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"5d02c0c4f3","type":"paragraph","text":"全年的生产任务提前六十天完成，海","index":56,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"7c258c3337","type":"paragraph","text":"水鱼总产量比去年同期提高23.1%。","index":57,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"54c575df04","type":"paragraph","text":"《本市今年海洋渔市场鱼货充足，出现繁荣景象”，“一天1972.12.30《解放日报》","index":58,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"308d4603a6","type":"paragraph","text":"业丰收》","index":59,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"587b8cbbcd","type":"paragraph","text":"一网捕到五万多斤鱼，可起网绳断，船长等4人跳下海去，在风浪中冒寒补","index":60,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"c4f033b1f0","type":"paragraph","text":"网，夺回了三万多斤带鱼”。《本市上半年海洋","index":61,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"23cd324e2b","type":"paragraph","text":"发现鱼群后，调动36对渔轮开赴渔场，1973.7.15《解放日报》渔业生产夺得丰","index":62,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"5338d3aefc","type":"paragraph","text":"“白产量达四十万斤，夺得了丰产”","index":63,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"893fcc2cd6","type":"paragraph","text":"收》","index":64,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"3ccc1e84d9","type":"paragraph","text":"如报载：多数量、大马力的海上机动船队以及先进的声纳探渔、灯光诱围技术，一网就是“三万多斤带鱼”，“十多万斤大黄鱼”，“日产量达四十万斤”；动就是“月产量比去年同期增加50%”，“全年的生产任务提前六十天完成”；具体还有“抢风前，追风尾”、淡季不淡，旺季更旺”的作业....这怎能不使水产品的产量有增无减呢！然而，正是这人的需要（需要孕育着贫变）面对物的生存；正是这人的聪明（聪明尚且不是智慧）面对物的繁衍，以致当这种需要和聪明转换成无往不胜的技术，面对自然生成的资源时；以致当人的理智尚未遭遇自然生态的报复，而处于背嗨状态时，这又怎能不种下导致自然资源衰退的褐根呢！故此，1970年至1973年的“捷报频传”（实为破坏性监捕），正是1974年至1976年产量滑落的启动（1974年后便不见上海报刊的相关报道），甚至是80年代后海洋渔业资源面临全面危机的因由。至于同期的长江河口渔业和内河渔业，也因“上海江段水质污染和滩涂变迁，破坏了上海江段的生态”；[15]乡镇工业的兴起和化肥、农药的使用，导致“大量水域遭受污染”而严","index":65,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"631f579df4","type":"paragraph","text":"PDG重菱缩。16]","index":66,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"08bed27efa","type":"paragraph","text":"正是立足在这个时空坐标上，完全可以断言上海地区的渔业资上海的河门和内河渔业资源曾相当丰富（徐建刚提供","index":67,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"4c4bd48216","type":"paragraph","text":"话11","index":68,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"20d87737ee","type":"paragraph","text":"被污染的苏州河源和生产链，在“文革”时期发生了断裂。当然，这不是指“文革”运动直接作用了、招致了这场断裂，而是指这场断裂的发生机缘与“文革”运动存在着种种间接的关联，如政治上坚持“为革命”、“为路线”生产的原则；生产上为弥补“停船”事故手70年代大规模投资更新设备等。所以，此在的确切说法应该是：多年积累的工农业生产和城乡发展与自然资源休养生息之间的矛盾，终于在“文革”时期爆发了。","index":69,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"63b28987f6","type":"paragraph","text":"二、供应与票证","index":70,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"9ca3a3a6d9","type":"paragraph","text":"生产主导市场，产量决定供应。下面请看上海“文革”时期水产品零售总量图：","index":71,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"517ca2eeca","type":"paragraph","text":"上海“文革”时期水产品零售总量图23","index":72,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"12b0120c1e","type":"paragraph","text":"19.516.15","index":73,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"f337bdafab","type":"paragraph","text":"17.2517.2520","index":74,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"6b4baf5215","type":"paragraph","text":"14.2","index":75,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"5e8ef66056","type":"paragraph","text":"17吨5","index":76,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"e253d3d8bb","type":"paragraph","text":"14.6万5","index":77,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"f4dbcf1c80","type":"paragraph","text":"12.1512.4515.95","index":78,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"83193e3590","type":"paragraph","text":"12.55S019661967196819691970197119721973197419751976","index":79,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"fb12c80852","type":"paragraph","text":"年份","index":80,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"572cedd0fe","type":"paragraph","text":"一水产品零售总量","index":81,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"d5974f44fa","type":"paragraph","text":"资料来源：上海市水产局《上海市水产统计资料汇编》。顾惠庭：《上海渔业志》，第243页。","index":82,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"14ca5758be","type":"paragraph","text":"如图：上海“文革”前期的水产品零售保持在年12万多吨。1970年后零售总量直线上升，至1974年甚至达到19万多吨，1975年后便开始下滑。其基本波动线与前述“资源一生产”链的关联相吻合，说明大自然的报复最终是要在“市场一供应”链上表现出来。然而，仔细比对又可发现上海水产品的零售货源量高于产量，比如1968年度，上海海洋渔业产量为5万多吨，零售量则为12万多吨；1974年度，上海海洋渔业产量为11万多吨，零售量则为19万多吨。此中缘由除了长江河口渔业和内河渔业的产量没有计算在内，更主要的是","index":83,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"c9c134bca4","type":"paragraph","text":"PDG江浙一带的水产品仍源源不断地供应上海，“文革”十年间的年度平均比例甚至高达总量的52.2%，17]与猪肉、禽蛋等副食品“全国保上海”的路径完全一致，只是在此不作赞述了","index":84,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"5474fee633","type":"paragraph","text":"为了保证市民购买水产品的需要，上海自1963年第三季度起，采用按地区人口比例分配的办法，向客区县（菜场）供货。请看表三","index":85,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"b3daecea94","type":"paragraph","text":"表三上海1964年与1967年度各区县水产品计划分配比例表","index":86,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"b985d6e25c","type":"paragraph","text":"单位：%区县黄浦虹口","index":87,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"dc4101cc0b","type":"paragraph","text":"南市杨浦|闸北静安|卢湾普陀徐汇！","index":88,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"0efe83c312","type":"paragraph","text":"长宁吴淞！闵行郊区市店年份","index":89,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"662bcdbec3","type":"paragraph","text":"11.59.09.08.07.16.75.51.81.04.90.8196410.412.411.9","index":90,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"f9552f124c","type":"paragraph","text":"5.10.611.312.09.3","index":91,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"924a7eca54","type":"paragraph","text":"7.96.85.71.91.5196710.1111.8","index":92,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"f0e8af442a","type":"paragraph","text":"8.37.7","index":93,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"8f8c0aef74","type":"paragraph","text":"资料来源：上海市水产公司供销公司档案；顾惠庭：《上海渔业志》，第257页。","index":94,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"9df5f11517","type":"paragraph","text":"说明：1.表中1964年度为当年2月9日调整的分配比例：表中1967年度为当年5月2日调整的分配比例。2.表中“郊区”一栏，具体指宝山、上海、嘉定、川沙四个近郊的城镇供应。3.表中“市店”，具体指位于福州路的市水产商店。","index":95,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"45bff477fb","type":"paragraph","text":"如表三所示，上海1967年的水产品分配比例量，在1964年的基础上作了调整，具体比例有所增长的是杨浦（0.5%）、闸北（0.3%）、普陀（0.8%）、徐汇（0.1%）、长宁（0.2%）、吴淞（0.1%）、闵行（0.5%）及郊区（0.2%）等行政区划。有所降低的则是黄浦（一0.3%）、虹口（—0.6%）、南市（一0.6%）、静安（一0.7%）、卢湾（一0.3%）及市店（一0.2%）等行政区划。很明显，在占总量2.7%的调整比例中，整个超动是从中心城区流向边缘城区（以与郊区接为标志），或者说是更多地流向工矿企业和劳动人民较为集中的区域，以致与“文革”时期各区人口的位序（杨浦→虹口→南市→黄浦→闸北→普陀→静安→卢湾→徐汇→长宁）保持了较高程度的一致。18]","index":96,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"a3cf544ffc","type":"paragraph","text":"关于上海水产品供应与票证关系的问题，时间跨度为1959年2月至1985年4月，长达26年，大致可分为四个阶段。","index":97,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"390f8bdbc1","type":"paragraph","text":"PDG","index":98,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"2d7fb4c3d2","type":"paragraph","text":"第一阶段：最初的票证。1959年前，上海水产品货源充裕，全币实行散开供应。1959年2月下旬（春节），上海开始凭票定量供应，即每人发鱼票1张，每张可买鱼10两（16两制，合312.5克）。至1963年春节，连续五年均实行凭票供应。此后，因渔业资源与生产情况良好，1963年1月原凭鱼券供应的水产罐头散开供应；继而6月1日起，水产熟食品敬开供应，同时，菜场卖鱼已不凭票或凭票不限量，鱼票回笼率低至20%”，19]故当年9月30日，上海水产品恢复散开供应。第一价段的特征是记录了从“敲开一凭票定量→恢复敲开”的轨迹。","index":99,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"a1d70fc301","type":"paragraph","text":"第二阶段：尬的散开。1963年10月后，上海水产品量然实行敬开供应，但品种比较单调，主要是带鱼和马贼，居民称之为“一长一短，一白一黑”。冬汛带鱼大量上市时，曾按牌价七折供应，甚至还奖励食油，伙食团则享受批发价（上海食品加工广则用带鱼为原料，制成调味食用鱼松投放市场）。1966年下半年，上海渔轮一度因“文革”运动“停产闹革命”，致使第三季度产量比去年同期减少43%，故从当年9月份起，上海水产品供应紧张，有时一大全市上市量仅50余吨。至1967年10月，上海水产品甚至超于脱销的边缘，市水产品公司只得压缩供应数量，平时每天供应市场90吨左右（海鲜50吨、咸十品25吨、淡水鱼15吨），周日为150吨，其实此数量尚不到正常年景供应量的一半。所以，尽管此阶段号称“敬开供应”，却因市场供应量严重菱缩，“菜场水产品摊排队最早，队伍最长，居民意见纷纷”。[20]为解决市场困难，上海自1969年3月下旬起，曾一度实行由菜场发票对口供应水产品。购买办法的改进，并不能求得供应量的增加。不久因居民有票仍买不到质量较好的鱼，只得取消该办法第二阶段的特征是事实上的供应短缺导致了市场紧张。[21]","index":100,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"ff782c3b38","type":"paragraph","text":"第三阶段：有计划的票证。1972年2月下旬起，上海水产品的总体供应已超缓和，但为解决市民求购优质品种鱼的需要，上海规定","index":101,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"449011c52b","type":"paragraph","text":"PDG居民分区按户、凭证（副食品购买证，即“菜卡”定点、定量、不定期每户供应水产品2市斤（当年，以海为原料的鱼魔制品水发鱼圆开始供应菜场，受到市民欢迎）。1973年春节时，市区居民按户发给花色鱼券和一般鱼券各一张，大户每户6市斤，小户每户4市斤，花色鱼和一般鱼各半供应（往后春节供应均参照此法）。1974年起，则取消大小户，实行凭证定点、定量、不定期，每次每户供应黄鱼和花色鱼1公斤（2市斤）的办法，其他品种鱼可随意购买。这种购买办法一直延续至“文革”运动终结，改革开放起始。第三阶段的特征是凭票证保证节日中优质鱼的供应。","index":102,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"a99f469dea","type":"paragraph","text":"上海市水产供销公司","index":103,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"21653eb2c5","type":"paragraph","text":"上海市水产供销公司日银料节日鱼票招联","index":104,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"064519337a","type":"paragraph","text":"节日铁节日鱼票团网春节（甲）","index":105,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"0a1f6149f1","type":"paragraph","text":"春节（乙m","index":106,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"450cf65f9d","type":"paragraph","text":"祥1985张","index":107,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"aed8df9941","type":"paragraph","text":"1985送","index":108,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"a58e7143e1","type":"paragraph","text":"第四阶段：最后的票证。自1980年8月起，市区居民不分大小户，凭证每次每户供应什鱼1公斤（2市斤），伙食团按核粮人数每人250克，一般20天至30天轮吃一次（货源多时，间隔时间缩短）。因凭票供应的水产品均为平价，所发生的政策性亏损，概由财政补贴。据统计，当年财政补贴达549万元。1982年2月起，上海实行计划定量供应与散开供应相结合；平价销售与议价销售相结合，具体规定市区和郊县市属户口每户每月凭证供应什鱼1公斤（2市斤），伙食团每人每月0.5公斤。计划定量供应的品种是150克以上的鱼，100克以上的带鱼以及梅鱼、鱼、马鱼、海等；散开供应的是小什鱼、马面鱼、青船等。议价水产品主要是优质鱼、虾、蟹等。1985年1月起，因凭证货源短缺，上海重新按常住户口，每人每月发放鱼票1张，每张供应250克。伙食团每人每月0.5公斤。结果，因当年年初市","index":109,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"d009b28e46","type":"paragraph","text":"PDG场货源不足，品种较差，许多居民凭票买不到鱼，意见很大。1985年4月13日起，上海水产品供应终于实行“价格放开，随行就市，按质论价，散开供应”。因由价格调节供求，市场形成高、中、低多层次消费，上市品种增多，供应趋于平稳，实施多年的财政补贴宣布取消。227第四阶段的特征是记录了票证政策走向解体的轨迹","index":110,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"1a1938e3bf","type":"paragraph","text":"三、供应与价格","index":111,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"2a50d0ce47","type":"paragraph","text":"接着，请通过三张统计表格（表四、表五与表六），看上海“文革”时期水产品供应的价格情况。先看表四","index":112,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"3d537a8e42","type":"paragraph","text":"表四上海“文革”时期市区水产品零售价格表（附1985年）","index":113,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"82818e3537","type":"paragraph","text":"单位：元/担（50公斤）","index":114,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"b9cc05173b","type":"paragraph","text":"鲫鱼","index":115,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"41bee98cf8","type":"paragraph","text":"乌贼鱼馒鱼青鱼草鱼链鱼年份大黄鱼小黄鱼带鱼","index":116,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"5ff2c2b424","type":"paragraph","text":"39.4135.0029.7824.3250.2738.5184.0074.0047.0084.001966","index":117,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"b4e6163700","type":"paragraph","text":"29.1524.3951.0039.00","index":118,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"d222f88ad0","type":"paragraph","text":"84.0074.0047.0084.00196739.6434.86","index":119,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"a4d9938191","type":"paragraph","text":"34.8729.9825.0751.0039.0084.0074.0047.0084.00196839.71196939.6734.8829.9325.1751.0039.00","index":120,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"0c55cea937","type":"paragraph","text":"84.0074.0047.0084.00197040.0035.0030.47","index":121,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"7b5e56c5ba","type":"paragraph","text":"26.0051.0039.0084.0074.0047.0084.00","index":122,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"1f97c3fec0","type":"paragraph","text":"26.0051.0039.0084.0040.0035.0030.48","index":123,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"cec5aac8bf","type":"paragraph","text":"74.0047.0084.001971197240.0035.0030.4826.0051.0039.00","index":124,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"b008cf8e6d","type":"paragraph","text":"84.0074.0047.0084.00","index":125,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"b332c09884","type":"paragraph","text":"35.0030.4826.0051.0039.0084.0074.0047.0084.00197340.00","index":126,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"0395f2c78c","type":"paragraph","text":"74.0047.0084.00197440.00","index":127,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"f9e486acda","type":"paragraph","text":"35.0030.4826.0051.0039.0084.00","index":128,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"33db57fa8d","type":"paragraph","text":"40.0035.0030.3726.0051.0039.0084.0074.0047.0084.001975","index":129,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"4a951f31ba","type":"paragraph","text":"40.0035.0030.5026.0051.0039.0084.00","index":130,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"1a8691d82f","type":"paragraph","text":"74.0047.0084.0019761985251.96158.8699.6894.83163.77126.23217.17","index":131,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"38c05a7bda","type":"paragraph","text":"165.2892.84196.26资料来源：顾惠庭：《上海渔业志》第274-278页：注杰：《上海价格志》第135137页。","index":132,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"fcaecdd4c0","type":"paragraph","text":"PDG","index":133,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"da8317d19b","type":"paragraph","text":"如表四所示，第一，文革”十年间，上海水产品价格基本处于冻结状态。除了大小黄鱼、带鱼、乌贼等品种的价格，略有每市斤一二分钱的调整，如1966年大黄鱼每市斤0.394元，1976年时每市斤0.40元；1966年带鱼每市斤0.298元，1976年时每市斤0.305元；1966年乌赋每市斤0.243元，1976年时每市斤0.260元等。其余如鱼（每市斤0.390元）、青鱼（每市斤0.840元）、草鱼（每市斤0.740元）、鱼（每市斤0.470元）、细鱼（每市斤0.840元）等均十年一个价，包括季节差价等均不作计算。尽管1972年3月国家曾统一提高了东海地区黄鱼和带鱼的收购价5%；1973年又适当提高淡水鱼收购价，但“购销价格基本保持在1963年的水平，导致较长时间水产品价格严重背离价值”。123]如此价格水平固然可以认作为不涨价，但联系“文革”时期全民性的低工资制，相互之间的外误也就在同一个象限里扯平了。","index":134,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"7bc7c300a9","type":"paragraph","text":"第二，恰恰因为长达十年的价格冻结，就如同压道的弹簧一旦摆脱，便猛地弹升起来。所以至1979年底价格放开后的统计：上海海水鱼零售价格平均提高28%；淡水鱼零售价格平均提高38%。本表特列改革开放后的1985年上海水产品零售价格以求比照——又是一个十年——海水鱼大黄鱼的价格翻了6倍多；带鱼、鱼等翻了3倍多；淡水鱼青鱼、鲫鱼等的价格都翻了2倍多。然而，其内里价格杠杆的调节和全民工资收人的增长，却使供求更超平衡，市场更趋稳定","index":135,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"95e76241a8","type":"paragraph","text":"再看表五：","index":136,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"7b4bd12266","type":"paragraph","text":"表五沪杭宁水产品零售价格对照表（以1973年为例）","index":137,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"a2f0ee41b5","type":"paragraph","text":"单位：元/担（50公斤）","index":138,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"f7797e5898","type":"paragraph","text":"南京","index":139,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"0182d062df","type":"paragraph","text":"杭上海","index":140,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"ba5cd0cc55","type":"paragraph","text":"州","index":141,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"363e493256","type":"paragraph","text":"规格品名","index":142,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"d90723b3a4","type":"paragraph","text":"比例价格","index":143,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"5a495cf79d","type":"paragraph","text":"价格","index":144,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"26ded3ff92","type":"paragraph","text":"比例","index":145,"publicationId":"440c8819-7c1b-4eaa-981b-2579bd8e1a1a","articleId":"df5720ae11"},{"id":"502854fa48","type":"paragraph","text":"价格","index":146,"publicationId":"4